Mission Orders

Argon-altered sikandari are damaging and stealing our research equipment. Eliminate {@LinkCreature:46#301$$argonomorph sikandaris}, {@LinkCreature:46#302$$argonomorph fiends}, {@LinkCreature:46#303$$argonomorph blood fiends}, and {@LinkCreature:46#304$$argonomorph jalmaraks}.

Report to the nearest coordinator when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation. Your guild is an inspiration to all!
